[SN]TITLE[SN]
Inmates injured in 'assault' at HMP Hewell

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An investigation has been launched after two prisoners were taken to hospital following an alleged assault at HMP Hewell.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police were called to the prison in Redditch, Worcestershire, at about 16:30 GMT on Thursday.
West Mercia Police said: "Two prisoners were subsequently taken to hospital with injuries that were not believed to be life-threatening."
An investigation is underway and police inquiries are ongoing.
